                                     <strong>KORRELYaCIYa VALYuTA: ONY ҚALAY PAYDALANU KEREK?</strong><p><span></span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span> </span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Kezіnde sauda naryғynda Foreks sөzsіz bayқalady әserі bіr valyutany basқa, sondyқtan, tіptі tәghіribelі maman almaydy taңdauғa valyutalyқ ghұp, ol tolyғymen tәuelsіz. Әserі valyuta tudyruy mүmkіn өsuі, sonday-aқ baғamynyң құldyrauy, ghәne olardyң қozғalysy dep ataydy korrelyaciey valyutalyқ ghұp. Үshіn ghan-ghaқty sipattau bұl process paydalanylady korrelyaciya koefficientі, қazіrgі diapazonynda -1 +1. Қaray koefficientіn bөlіnedі oң ghәne terіs korrelyaciya. </span></p><h3><span><b>Atalғan brokerler sauda үshіn Foreks:</b></span></h3><ul><li><span></span><a><b>ALPARI</b></a></li><li><span></span><a><b>ROBOFOREX</b></a></li><li><span></span><a><b>Forex4You</b></a></li><li><span></span><a><b>AMarkets</b></a></li><li><span></span><a><b>InstaForex</b></a></li></ul><p><span>Treyderge niet bіldіrgen dұrys uaқytta kіru үshіn ұstanymyn қaghet korrelyaciya valyutalyқ ghұp. Sonday-aқ, ol қaghet emes ghol ashu mәmіlelerdі edі isklyuchali bіr-bіrіn. Kөptegen brokerler kөrsetetіn treyderam taldau ghasaydy, grafikter men kesteler қozғalysynyң valyutalyқ ghұp tәuekelderdі barynsha azaytu үshіn, өytkenі shyғyndar boyynsha bіr valyutada өteledі paydany, satudan alynғan ekіnshі. Degenmen, қaupі bar alshaқtyқ valyutalyқ ghұp, tіkeley korreliruyuschih belgіlі sәtke deyіn, ghәne bұl eskeru қaghet kezіnde sauda. Bұl, әsіrese үshіn treyderler, olar soңyna deyіn tүsіnbeydі, mұnday obligaciyalar federalydyқ қaryz emes, bіledі, olardy dұrys қoldana bіlu.</span></p><h2><span><b>TӘUEKELDERDІ ӘRTARAPTANDYRU</b></span></h2><p><span>Sonymen қatar, ұmytuғa bұl korrelyaciya absolyuttі boluy mүmkіn emes – ol sonday-aқ kөmektesedі treyderge өzіnің tәuekelderіn әrtaraptandyruғa. Mysaly, treyder mүmkіn өsіruge ashylatyn atyndaғy ұstanymyn үmіtpen dep naryғy poydet ghoғary, bіraқ dana sheshіm bolady bөlіnuі satyp alynatyn ghәne satylatyn valyuta kөlemіn ekі-үsh ghұptarymen, bar қazіrgі uaқytta ghoғary kөrsetkіsh tіkeley korrelyaciya. Osylaysha, treyder eskertedі yқtimal keleңsіz әserі skachkov valyutalyқ kurs.</span></p><h2><span><b>PRINCIPTERІ BAYLANYSTY KORRELYaCIEY VALYuTALYҚ GhҰP</b></span></h2><p><span>Sәttі sauda naryғynda treyderge meңgerіluі negіzgі principterі, baylanysty korrelyaciey valyutalyқ ghұp. Sonymen қatar, өte maңyzdy bіlu degenіmіz ne heshreyt. Өzderі maңyzy bar korrelyaciya nepostoyanny ghәne өzgerіp, kүn sanap, sondyқtan ghol berіlmeydі ghұmys іsteu statichnym indikatory. Taңdau қaghet әr tүrlі shemalary ghұmys kezіnde қysқa merzіmdі ghәne ұzaқ merzіmdі aralyқtarda ghұmys. Sanyna negіzgі sebepterdі terbelіster valyuta naryғynda ghatady:</span></p><ul><li><span>Maңyzdy ekonomikalyқ kүyzelіster;</span></li><li><span>Өzgertu sayasi kүshterdі;</span></li><li><span>Neprognoziruemye oқiғalar әser etetіn makroekonomikaғa.</span></li></ul><p><span>Mұnday ghaғdaylarda treyderge keledі tolyқ өz ghosparlaryn қayta қarauғa қatysty satyp alu nemese valyutany satu. Alu үshіn valyutalyқ kalykulyaciyasyn, oғan қaghet bolady paydalana analitikoy өz brokerdің nemese іzdeu talap etіletіn mәnі ghelі, alayda, soңғy ghaғdayda, mүmkіndіk bar natolknutysya na dұrys nemese neaktualynoe mәnі.</span></p><p><span>Sonday-aқ, kөrіңіz korrelyaciyasyn esepteu өz betіnshe nemese arnayy kalykulyator treyderdің. Sұraudy өz erkіmen ghіbergen kezde esepteu treyder alady mұқiyat taldau ghәne razobratysya v cifrah nәtighesіnde aluғa naқty ghәne dұrys nәtighe beredі. Baғdarlama Excel kөmektesedі өtkіzu esebі ghyldam ghәne dәl үshіn bұl ghay ғana importtauғa maңyzy bar қalanyң ekі valyutalyқ ghұp eskere otyryp, talap etіletіn uaқyt aralyғy. Үshіn orta merzіmdі interval paydalanylady kөrsetkіshterі 1 aydan 12 ayғa deyіn. Esep ayyrysu korrelyaciya aқsha құraldary auystyryldy ovshory, bіrneshe erekshelenedі ghoғaryda berіlgen.</span></p><div></div>
